66666\">:</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"> // select 等待成功, 有描述符准备好了, 这里就是 _listensock 准备好了, 可以开始进行连接做读写服务了</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">                    _log</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">LogMessage</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">DEBUG</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> \"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">get a new link, </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A65E2B;--shiki-dark:#C99076\">%s</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A65E2B;--shiki-dark:#C99076\"> %d</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> __FILE__</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> __LINE__</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">                    // 等待后续继续编码...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">                    break</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">            }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">        }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><